==Russian==
===Etymology===
Originated from a joke ([[internet phenomenon]]) at http://www.anekdot.ru &mdash "[[хорониль|Хоронили]] [[тёща|тёщу]] &mdash [[рвать|порвали]] [[два#Russian|два]] баяна" (when they buried my mother-in-law, they broke two accordions).

===Noun===
'''баян''' (baján) {{m}}

#''(Internet slang)'' [[joke]]
#: "Баян! Давай [[исчо]]!" &mdash; It was a joke! Come on, already!
# large [[accordion]]

